Egon Brecher https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Egon_Brecher 0 Egon Brecher (18 February 1880 – 12 August 1946) was an Austria-Hungary-born actor and director, who also served as the chief director of Vienna's Stadttheater, before entering the motion picture industry.
